======================================================================

  Build dependencies
  ------------------

  * Apache Maven >= 3.5.2

  Packaging as a web application
  ------------------------------

  In order to generate an EAR archive that could be deployed on your
  application server of choice, issue the following command. You will
  find the generated .ear file inside the package folder.

  Change ${version} and ${environment} to suit your needs.

  $ mvn clean package -Drevision=${version} -P ${environment}
